product_short_description.displayValue:
Sams Choice Italia Fusilloni Pasta traditionally hails from Naples and is made with 100% selected high-quality Italian durum wheat. Made with a recipe passed down for generations, this pasta delivers authentic taste that is quick and easy to prepare. It is traditionally made with bronze dies to give it a rougher surface that better absorbs sauces and give you a more traditional and delicious pasta. Simply boil it in water with the easy-to-follow instructions on the package and top it with stir-fried vegetables or meat to create a mouth-watering pasta dinner. This fusilloni is produced by one of the few pasta factories left that controls the complete production process from the selection of durum wheat to the finished product.

Sourced and imported directly from Italy, Sams Choice Italia brings you the best cuisine that Italy has to offer. Enjoy fine, authentic ingredients, classically delicious recipes, and full flavor in every bite. We offer you a carefully curated assortment that is both innovative and enticing. Sams Choice products are inspired by our proud heritage and are trusted today by the millions of customers us across the world.
